jasperReport.name: daily_income
jasperReport.queryString:
Select b_site.site_full_name as hospital_name ,t_patient.patient_hn as hn ,substring(t_billing_invoice.t_billing_invoice_date_time,12,5) as receipt_time ,f_patient_prefix.patient_prefix_description || t_patient.patient_firstname || ' ' || t_patient.patient_lastname as fullname ,b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id as debt ,t_billing_invoice.billing_invoice_total as paid ,b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id as plan ,t_visit.f_visit_type_id as visit_type From t_visit inner join t_billing_invoice on (t_billing_invoice.t_visit_id = t_visit.t_visit_id and t_billing_invoice.billing_invoice_active <> '0' and substr(t_billing_invoice.t_billing_invoice_date_time,1,16) >= $P{datestart} and substr(t_billing_invoice.t_billing_invoice_date_time,1,16) <= $P{dateend} and t_billing_invoice.billing_invoice_total <> '0' and (t_visit.f_visit_status_id = '2' or t_visit.f_visit_status_id = '3')) inner join t_patient on t_visit.t_patient_id = t_patient.t_patient_id left join f_patient_prefix on (f_patient_prefix.f_patient_prefix_id = t_patient.f_patient_prefix_id) inner join t_visit_payment on (t_visit_payment.t_visit_payment_id = t_billing_invoice.t_payment_id and t_visit_payment.visit_payment_active <> '0' and t_visit_payment.visit_payment_priority ='0' ) inner join b_contract_plans on (b_contract_plans.b_contract_plans_id = t_visit_payment.b_contract_plans_id) inner join b_rpnk_map_plan on (b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_std_id = b_contract_plans.b_contract_plans_id) , b_site where b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '01' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '02' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '03' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '04' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '05' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '06' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '07' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '08' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '09' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '10' or b_rpnk_map_plan.rpnk_map_plan_ref_id = '11'
Order By t_billing_invoice.t_billing_invoice_date_time
